features: 【Multi-Pocket Design】: The exterior of the car visor organizer is made up of 6 card holder pockets and 1 glasses clip. The interior is an oversized pocket with two deep side slip pockets and 4 storage locations which are secured by an elastic band. The large 11.41 x 5.90 x 1.18 inch is designed to perfectly hold the small items in your daily life such as cell phones, sunglasses, cords, documents, cards, pens, charger cables, headphones, CDs and more.

【Durable PU Material】: The car storage bag is made of durable PU leather, which is not only odorless and very wear-resistant, but also can blend perfectly with your car's interior and look more advanced. It has a very delicate and comfortable feel. Even if it is exposed to the sun for a long time, it will not crack or fade. The metal zipper is very textured and shiny, and it will be silky smooth without snagging as you open or close it.

【Install & Remove】: The back of the visor organizer has two tough and flexible elastic straps with Velcro, so you can easily secure it to your visor. In addition, the elastic straps are freely adjustable, so you can remove it very quickly when you don't need it. It provides more storage space for the interior of your car and keeps it clean and organized.

【Easy to Clean】: Car interior storage bags are washable. When used for a long time you may find stains. Don't worry, you just need to wash it with water and dry it, and it will be back as good as new. This visor organizer is a universal design that is widely available for most car, suv and truck visors.

【Friendly Service】: We strive to constantly innovate to meet our customers' needs and provide them with better products. We are committed to manufacturing first-class products. Please contact us if there is anything about which you are unsure or dissatisfied.
